'''Sofia Amara''' (yavutse ku ya 25 Gicurasi 1968) ni umunyamakuru w’umufaransa wavukiye muri [[Maroke|Maroc]] akaba n'umuyobozi wa firime.

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Amara yavukiye i Casablanca mu 1968. Yarangije muri kaminuza ya Yorodani afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bumenyi bwa politiki no muri IEP i Paris mu 1996. Amara yatangiye umwuga we wumwuga nkumunyamakuru muburasirazuba bwo hagati kumiyoboro itandukanye na radio. Yagaragaje ibyabaye nka Intifada ya mbere y'Abanyapalestine, igitero cya Koweti na Iraki, no kugaruka kwa Yasser Arafat muri Gaza. <ref>https://www.babelio.com/auteur/Sofia-Amara/330299</ref>

Amara yatanze raporo ku Isoko ry'Abarabu muri Egiputa, kandi afungwa kabiri hamwe n'abigaragambyaga i Cairo. Yakoze documentaire ku ntambara yo muri Siriya kuva yatangira mu 2011.  Muri 2014, Amara yasohoye igitabo ''Infiltrée dans l'enfer syrien: du Printemps de Damas à l'Etat islamique'' aho yasabye ko igihugu cya kisilamu cya Iraki na Levant (ISIL) mubyukuri byari umufatanyabikorwa wa Bashar al-Assad . <ref>https://www.franceculture.fr/oeuvre-infiltree-dans-l-enfer-syrien-de-sofia-amara</ref> Mosul amaze kubohorwa muri 2017, Amara yabaye umwe mu banyamakuru ba mbere b’abagore binjiye mu mujyi hamwe n’ingabo za Iraki. 

Muri 2017, yayoboye documentaire ''Yabuze Abana ba Califa'', yerekanaga abana bafite imyaka umunani bogejwe n'ubwonko kandi bahabwa imyitozo yintwaro. <ref>https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/isis-forces-children-young-five-10412834</ref> Yakiriye igihembo cya AMADE mu iserukiramuco rya TV rya Monte-Carlo.  Muri 2018, Amara yasohoye igitabo ''Bagdadi, Khalifa w'iterabwoba'' . Harimo ibiganiro bye n'uwahoze ari umugore n'umukobwa wa Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi,, umuyobozi wa ISIL. Igitabo cyasuzumye izamuka ry'ubutegetsi bwa al-Baghdadi n'ingaruka zaryo ku isi. <ref>https://www.france24.com/en/20181022-interview-sofia-amara-islamic-state-group-terrorism-women-leader-baghdadi-ex-wife</ref>

Amara ifite icyicaro i Beirut . Muri 2019, yanenze Perezida wa Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika [[Donald Trump]] kuba adafite politiki yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati kandi yirengagiza ihohoterwa rya guverinoma z'Abarabu. Amara yavuze ko umwanzuro uhangayikishije cyane mu mpeshyi y’Abarabu ari uko "hari abayobozi bashinzwe ibibazo bakora bashingiye ku nyungu zabo bwite zihinduka kandi rimwe na rimwe zikabarwa nabi." 

